ui ont oeuvrés sur cette version :</h4>\n<ul id="wp-people-group-validators" class="wp-people-group compact">\n<li id="wp-person-momo360modena" class="wp-person"><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/momo360modena"><img class="gravatar" src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/bd9516b368db97643f1cff5bf4c82123?s=30" alt="Amaury Balmer" /></a> <a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/momo360modena">Amaury Balmer</a></li>\n<li id="wp-person-xibe" class="wp-person"><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xibe"><img class="gravatar" src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c16970a350d2de8ced3017a5a8514969?s=30" alt="Xavier Borderie" /></a> <a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/xibe">Xavier Borderie</a></li>\n<li class="wp-person"><a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ben-kenobi"><img class="gravatar" src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/7bb495a607f1f7e4a231404a42b81936?s=30" alt="Benoit Catherineau" /></a> <a class="web" href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ben-kenobi">Benoît Catherineau</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p class="wp-credits-list">&#8230; ainsi que<a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/ado666"> ado666</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/dakotapearl">dakotapearl</a>, <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/fge0">Franck Gervais</a> et <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/jaddle">jaddle</a>.</p>\n<p class="wp-credits-list">C&rsquo;est grâce à eux que la version française est disponible en quasi simultanéité que la version originale. Merci à eux !</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 class="wp-credits-list">Ils en parlent aussi&#8230;</h2>\n<ul>\n<li class="wp-credits-list"><a href="https://wordpress.org/news/2014/12/dinah/">WordPress.org</a> (dont est tiré l&rsquo;article ci-dessus)</li>\n<li class="wp-credits-list"><a href="http://wptavern.com/wordpress-4-1-dinah-released">WP Tavern</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=wwuVe9q-5x0:h27tNRVwt-U:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Wor